data.description: Don't pass this one up! Beautifully updated Ranch home in Riverside neighborhood. One level living in main house includes 3 bedrooms and 2 Full Baths. An additional Bedroom/in-law suite/exercise room with Full Bath located in Detached large 2 car garage. This home has it all with the comfort of family room with fireplace and built in cabinets/wine fridge to the updated modern kitchen with custom cabinetry, granite counters and SS appliances. Bathrooms remodeled too! But wait, if you enjoy being outdoors, you'll love the backyard oasis with screened in porch, brick paver patio includes firepit and Hot Tub...all professionally landscaped and private!  You can enjoy the private Riverside Beach too. Conveniently located near shopping, restaurants, I-64 and James River Bridge, nestled behind CNU.
